JSP Compilation Support for Maven 2

 Provides support to precompile your JSPs and have them included into your WAR file.
 
 Version 2 of the JSP compilation support includes a pluggable JSP compiler implementation,
 which current allows different versions of the Tomcat Jasper compiler to be used as needed.

* Maven Plugin

 * {{{jspc-maven-plugin/index.html}jspc-maven-plugin}}: JSP Compilation support for Maven 2.
 
 []

* JSP Compilers

 In version 2 of the JSP plugin for Maven 2, the JSP compiler implementation is pluggable.
 Currently the following compilers are supported:

 * {{{jspc-compilers/jspc-compiler-tomcat5/index.html}Tomcat 5 Compiler}}: Uses Tomcat 5.5.15 Jasper compiler.
 
 * {{{jspc-compilers/jspc-compiler-tomcat6/index.html}Tomcat 6 Compiler}}: Uses Tomcat 6.0.18 Jasper compiler.
 
 []

